  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">HRFT: Strengthening Prevention of Torture</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This is in the form of continuation of a previous grant given to HRFT in 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017 and 2018. The HRFT gives treatment and rehabilitation to torture survivors and their families. It is foreseen that there will be 450 new applicants in 2019. It is also expected that the treatment of existing 200 torture survivors will continue. They will expand their rehabilitation services across Turkey and make it easier for torture survivors who are living in the cities where there is no HRFT</narrative>
  </description>
